  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He could be also in Tel Aviv a chief rabbi, but because of the Zionism, between the religious and non-religious, so probably that was the main reason.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the way I heard, he couldn't become the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now he was sent to Poland, with his family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, whoever was sent to Poland never came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the Munkatsh rabbi had such a connection in city hall.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, before the Hungarian came in, and even during the Hungarian, they gave him big respect, because he's a very educated, smart man.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had the connection to send a Hungarian officer, to Poland, to dress up his son-in-law for a Hungarian officer and to bring him back from Poland.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This particular rabbi, this son-in-law, as they brought him back, he knew he cannot exist anymore in Munkatsh.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they send him up-- also, for a lot of money-- to Budapest, the capital town of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father had a-- a chance to talk to the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he ask his advice, what would you suggest me?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Should I make the operation?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or shall I go to the forced labor?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this rabbi advised him, operation, we have always time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To go for a knife, and this is not so sexful-- successful, those days, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was not so advanced, like today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he left the hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he took the chance, instead of to go under a knife, he will go to forced labor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a miracle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A few days later, it came out that this year's, or those people who were in this particular year born, they don't have to go to this forced labor.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's how he survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
